|Reagent Recipies										                                                            |
|_______________________________________________________________________________________________|
It would be nice to see recipies created and added to various professions that would allow for the creation of 
the reagents that can be purchased at vendors. This would not include reagents such as "Light Feather", but rather 
reagents such as "Demonic Figurine" for the Jewlcrafting profession and "Teleport Rune" & "Portal Rune" 
for the Inscription profession.
