 _______________________________________________________________________________________________
|Translocational Escape - Spell												                                       		|
|_______________________________________________________________________________________________|
It would be nice to see a $spell that required a reagent, able to be crafted using inscription;
This $spell would activate the $spell_effect triggered by the use of a "Scroll of Recall" $item;
The $spell_effect that I have in mind only occurs in retail wow if the player using the $item is over level 40,
-and teleports the user of the $item to a random location. 
